text: Teddy, apparently you haven't been reading my comments about federal legislation on @realmoney I have consistently written that the chance of cannabis passage was de minimis and far less than consensus view. Do your homework better before criticizing. Enjoy the weekend.

@realmoney @dougkass @SeabreezeLP Written on July 12, 2022 11:55 AM EDT DOUG KASS Possibly the Worst Timing on Bank Stock Price Target Reductions Today and yesterday, Morgan Stanley (MS) and several other sell side research departments lowered their

price targets on the large money center banks - after a crippling price decline over the last two months and only days ahead of 2Q2022 EPS releases. They may be right in their conclusions and I might be totally wrong on my bullish financial thesis - but, regardless, there is

very little value in this week's downgrades. The weak state of Wall Street research is one of the reasons that I prefer to do my own analysis and not rely on them. @jimcramer @tomkeene @ferrotv @lisaabramowicz1 @SaraEisen @riskreversal @guyadami @ScottWapnerCNBC @business
